{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"value"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SQ","text":"Equatable"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"transform"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV","text":"Transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A value to monitor for changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"value"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The transformation to apply to transactions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within this view.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"transform"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all transactions used within the view whenever ","type":"text"},{"code":"value","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Consider three identical views controlled by a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"button that changes all three simultaneously:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The first view animates rotating the “Rotation” ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference"},{"text":" view by 360","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"degrees.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The second uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to change the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“Rotation\\nModified” "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" view animation by a factor of 2."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to disable animations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced” "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code implements these animations:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction(value: flag) { t in","                        t.animation =","                            t.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction(value: flag) { t in","                        t.disableAnimations = true","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/LabeledContentStyleConfiguration","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/LabeledContentStyleConfiguration\/Label-swift.struct"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"value","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SQ","text":"Equatable","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"